Hiya Kristin
   
  I have some time tonight so listening to your files here.
   
  File : /Kristin's Files/DONT CRY PLEASE PLEASE DONT CRY.wav 

  In this one I hear a lil different "Dont cry we want peace talk. Talk to kris tin" but overall same message behind it.
   
  File : /Kristin's Files/Protect you.wav 
  This one I also hear a tad different "if we can listen (what?) protect you"
   
  File : /Kristin's Files/Tell Them Hello.wav 
  I heard in this one. "Help you settle - yes - Hello Mom"
  I threw it in my ST filter and it got rid of some of the static at the end on the hello mom part for my ears so I will attach it here for you. It just made the statement I heard less drowned out by static tho I am used to hearing thru it. 
   
  As always what you hear is more important than what I hear.
   
  And my pc is choking up now so attaching the filtered file then gotta reboot.
   
  Misty
